                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I know this handkerchief—it</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184508180006"></xptr>
               <p>has never been out of my possession since I bought it in the East Indies—I always wash it myself when I wash my hands—here is a mark on it where I spilt some ink about sixteen months ago—I had two more of this pattern.</p>
